
This directory contains a few miscellaneous files that document various
parts of Capriccio.  This is by no means comprehensive documentation, but
hopefully it will help get people started.  ;-)

   apache-build       Notes on building apache with Capriccio
   build-berkeleydb   Notes on building Berkeley DB with Capriccio
   nptl-biuld         Notes on building NPTL
   using-cil          Information on how to use CIL with Capriccio
   html               Some HTML/gif format blocking graphs, generated from
                      running applications.

Rob von Behren <jrvb@cs.berkeley.edu>


